<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Transaction Confirmed</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div
      style="font-family: sans-serif; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;"
    >
      <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <h2 style="color: #4F46E5;">Transaction Confirmed</h2>
      </div>

      <div
        style="background-color: #f8f8f8; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;"
      >
        <p>Hi {{username}},</p>
        <p>Great news! Your transaction for <strong>{{eventName}}</strong> has been confirmed.</p>

        <div
          style="background-color: #fff; border-left: 4px solid #4F46E5; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0;"
        >
          <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>Transaction ID:</strong> {{transactionId}}</p>
        </div>

        <p>Your tickets are now ready. You can access them from your account dashboard.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="margin: 24px 0; text-align: center;">
        <a
          href="https://yourdomain.com/my-tickets"
          style="background-color: #4F46E5; color: white; padding: 12px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; display: inline-block;"
        >
          View My Tickets
        </a>
      </div>

      <div
        style="margin-top: 30px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 20px; font-size: 14px; color: #666;"
      >
        <p>We're excited to have you at the event! If you have any questions, please contact us.</p>
        <p>Thank you for using our platform.</p>
        <p>Best regards,<br /><strong>Ticket Team</strong></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>